name: Funky Jungle Siege
description:
This is a game to test your limits. Interactive that boost the level of confidence you have. To play this game you need to have 100 percent of stragegy game to beat your opponent. An two player battle to win all, ever strategy is needed to surpasses your enemy and win it all. The game struck you with different maps, that is very interactive when playing and different paths to play with. Character with different mechanics and sizes to play with. 

ALWAYS REMEMBER ! BEAT THE MEAT!
